# Provide Real File Links

## Description
Give links to the real files, not x.md.

## Examples
✅ Good:
- "See src/components/Button.tsx"
- "Check lib/utils/helpers.js"
- "Review tests/unit/User.test.ts"

❌ Bad:
- "See x.md"
- "Check the documentation"
- "Review the test file"

## Implementation
- Use actual file paths
- Reference specific files
- Provide complete file locations
- Avoid placeholder references
